---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Turbo Puffin — Built for the agentic web.</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Turbo Puffin builds companies that treat agents as first-class users — not as an afterthought, not as a feature. From the ground up." />
  <meta property="og:title" content="Turbo Puffin" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Turbo Puffin builds companies that treat agents as first-class users — not as an afterthought, not as a feature. From the ground up." />
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://turbopuffin.com" />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <script defer data-site="qknee4maxdqqhpyva2cb0og9" src="https://lets.measure.events/tracker.js"></script>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    :root {
      --bg: #0D0D0D;
      --text: #F0F0ED;        /* WCAG AAA — 16.9:1 on bg */
      --secondary: #D4D4CF;   /* WCAG AAA — 11.5:1 on bg */
      --muted: #C5C5C0;       /* WCAG AAA — 9.9:1 on bg */
      --accent: #E8611A;      /* Braun orange — CTA only */
      --card-bg: #141414;
      --card-border: #222222;
      --divider: #1C1C1C;
    }

    html {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    /* ── Header ── */
    header {
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--divider);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .logo {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .logo-mark {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1;
    }

    /* ── Main layout ── */
    main {
      flex: 1;
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
      width: 100%;
    }

    /* ── Hero ── */
    .hero {
      padding: 5rem 0 4rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--divider);
    }

    .hero-eyebrow {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 6vw, 3.5rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      line-height: 1.1;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .hero-lead {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: var(--secondary);
      max-width: 560px;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .cta-primary {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.375rem;
      background: transparent;
      color: #FF9A3C;           /* ~9:1 on #0D0D0D — WCAG AAA ✓ */
      border: 2px solid var(--accent);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.9375rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: background 0.15s ease, color 0.15s ease;
    }

    .cta-primary:hover {
      background: rgba(232, 97, 26, 0.10);
    }

    /* ── Philosophy section ── */
    .section {
      padding: 4rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--divider);
    }

    .section-label {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .section h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      line-height: 1.2;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .section p {
      font-size: 1.0625rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: var(--secondary);
    }

    /* ── Portfolio ── */
    .portfolio {
      padding: 4rem 0;
    }

    .portfolio-header {
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .portfolio-header h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    .cards {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--card-bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 2rem;
      transition: border-color 0.15s ease;
    }

    .card:hover {
      border-color: #2E2E2E;
    }

    .card-name {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
    }

    .card-tagline {
      font-size: 0.8125rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 0.875rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }

    .card-desc {
      font-size: 0.9375rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--secondary);
    }

    /* ── Footer ── */
    footer {
      padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--divider);
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    footer p {
      font-size: 0.8125rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    /* ── Mobile ── */
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .hero {
        padding: 3.5rem 0 3rem;
      }
      .section, .portfolio {
        padding: 3rem 0;
      }
      .card {
        padding: 1.5rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <a href="/" class="logo" aria-label="Turbo Puffin">
      <span class="logo-mark">Turbo Puffin</span>
    </a>
  </header>

  <main>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="hero">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Agentic-native software</span>
      <h1>Built for the agentic web.</h1>
      <p class="hero-lead">Turbo Puffin builds companies that treat agents as first-class users — not as an afterthought, not as a feature. From the ground up.</p>
      <a href="#portfolio" class="cta-primary">See what we're building →</a>
    </section>

    <!-- Philosophy -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="section-label">Why agentic-native</div>
      <h2>The next layer is being built now.</h2>
      <p>The web was built for humans. APIs were built for developers. The next layer — the one being assembled right now — is built for agents. Software that reads your analytics, monitors your metrics, and acts on your behalf. Most tools were not designed for this. Ours are.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Portfolio -->
    <section class="portfolio" id="portfolio">
      <div class="portfolio-header">
        <div class="section-label">Portfolio</div>
        <h2>What we're building</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="cards">

        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-name">Measure.events</div>
          <div class="card-tagline">Privacy-first analytics, built for the agentic web.</div>
          <p class="card-desc">Analytics your agents can actually use. Native agent interface lets your AI query traffic, understand trends, and surface insights — no dashboard required. Privacy-first by design.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-name">PropFirmDeck</div>
          <div class="card-tagline">The definitive prop trading firm comparison.</div>
          <p class="card-desc">Side-by-side comparisons of prop trading firms — rules, payouts, drawdown limits, funding tiers. Built for serious traders who need the facts, fast.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-name">ForGeorgetown</div>
          <div class="card-tagline">Georgetown, TX — hyperlocal and human.</div>
          <p class="card-desc">Hyperlocal news and community coverage for Georgetown, Texas. Real reporting on city council, local business, development, and what actually matters to the people who live here.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-name">Turbo Puffin Terminal</div>
          <div class="card-tagline">Proprietary trading infrastructure.</div>
          <p class="card-desc">A purpose-built trading terminal for the way professional traders actually work. DOM-first, fast, and built on real-time Rithmic infrastructure. Internal tooling, done right.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>© 2026 Turbo Puffin, LLC · Georgetown, TX · <a href="mailto:hello@turbopuffin.com" style="color: var(--muted); text-decoration: underline;">hello@turbopuffin.com</a></p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
